01ebae9acde59ac9aadd94350911e485352c1a7e.query:
SELECT "A".id          AS account_id,
       "AS".public_id  AS "account_session_public_id?",
       "AS".user_agent AS "account_session_user_agent?"
FROM account AS "A"
         LEFT JOIN account_session AS "AS" ON "A".id = "AS".account_id
WHERE "A".public_id = $1
  AND "A".deleted IS NULL
  AND "AS".deleted IS NULL;

353487abd4351cf9826ae994d40fc240774779b3.query:
SELECT A.id             AS account_id,
       AP.password_hash AS "account_password_hash?"
FROM account AS A
         LEFT JOIN account_password AS AP ON A.id = AP.account_id
WHERE A.username = $1
  AND AP.deleted IS NULL;
